Horses being monitored: 35
Humans exposed: 26
Humans sick: 0
Humans dead: 0

Once again, I extend appreciation to Storm Standford
<storm.stanford@gmail.com> for assistance and for summary tables.

We sincerely hope the exposed people remain healthy and that there
are no human deaths. Veterinarians and horse owners are on the front
lines of defense with this disease, are those most at risk, and most
often the first exposed - Mod.TG]
